title: deleted unused code - uploadActivity, declaration of uploadActivity in manifest,…

title: added shadow 9 patch for shadow below the header of templateHeador listView…
message: added shadow 9 patch for shadow below the header of templateHeador listView ,ie.e below the layout that contains edittext for author and template name..

title: solved force close issue for deleting quiz item and then clicking on expand…
message: solved force close issue for deleting quiz item and then clicking on expand button for other item in list since the item for deleted position do not exist but the count for currentPosition was still referring to it.

title: remoed unused code from templateActivity and made optimisations to list by…
message: remoed unused code from templateActivity and made optimisations to list by removing margin and adding padding instead to listview..so that when listview scroll, there is no gap between listview and toolbar and at the same time, both appear distinguished as toolbar has drop shadow below it...So that effect looks good.

title: made an xml for toolbar common to all activities and added drop shadow to…
message: made an xml for toolbar common to all activities and added drop shadow to toolbar to add material design features...removed onClick=true from cardviews in templateActivity because listView was not getting touch as cardView was consuming it..Ripple is working fine as before now also

title: removed floating action button library and added google design support library…
message: removed floating action button library and added google design support library which inlcudes floating action button, navigation view, snackbar and many other things...This new floating action button has better and simpler usage and has ripple also. added plus icon image for the fab icon.

title: changed navigation drawer to make it material design and also made gradle build…
message: changed navigation drawer to make it material design and also made gradle build changes to enable new Instant Run feature in android studio version 2 developer preview

title: corrected a bug that was causing force close when after removing an item from…
message: corrected a bug that was causing force close when after removing an item from the template editor activity list..caused error on clicking button in action bar..

title: made the gradle compile version to latest version - 23 since if user has support…
message: made the gradle compile version to latest version - 23 since if user has support version 23, then compiling against version 22 gives error....material dialogs library used was no longer working from original gradle...chnaged it and due to latest version, chnaged some code related to Theme files of that library.
